-- MOVES-Strategic Insight hires Shiv Taneja from Cerulli Associates
-- 
-- Mon Sep 15, 2014 12:06PM EDT
-- None



Sept 15 (Reuters) - Industry research and business intelligence provider Strategic Insight said it named Shiv Taneja as senior managing director of global research, to spearhead the expansion of the company's services to the mutual fund industry.

He joins from Cerulli Associates, where he was a founding member of the company's non-US research business. Taneja will report to Avi Nachmany, the company's co-founder and director of research.